quran[11{c,v,t}:
2,6,"jin logon ne ( inn baton ko tasleem karne se ) inkaar kar diya, unn ke liye yaksaa hai, khuwa tum inhen khabardaar karo ya nah karo, behar haal woh maan-ne walay nahi hain"
2,7,Allah ne un ke dilon aur un ke kaanon par mohar laga di hai aur un ki aankhon par parda par gaya hai woh sakht saza ke mustahiq hain
2,8,"baaz log aisay bhi hain jo kehte hain ke hum Allah par aur akhirat ke din par imaan laaye hain, halaank Dur haqeeqat woh momin nahi hain"
2,9,"woh Allah aur imaan laane walon ke sath dhoka baazi kar rahay hain, magar darasal woh khud apne aap hi ko dhokay mein daal rahay hain aur inhen is ka shaoor nahi hai"
2,10,"un ke dilon mein aik bemari hai jisay Allah ne aur ziyada barha diya, aur jo jhoot woh boltay hain, is ki Padaash mein un ke liye dard naak saza hai"
2,11,jab kabhi un se kaha gaya ke zameen par fasaad barpaa nah karo to unhon ne yahi kaha ke hum to islaah karne walay hain
2,12,khabardaar! haqeeqat mein yahi log mufsid hain magar inhen shaoor nahi hai
2,13,"aur jab un se kaha gaya jis terhan dosray log imaan laaye hain isi terhan tum bhi imaan lao to unhon ne yahi jawab diya"" kya hum bewaqfoon ki terhan imaan layein ?"" khabardaar! haqeeqat mein to yeh khud bewaqoof hain, magar yeh jantay nahi hain"
2,14,"jab yeh ahal imaan se mlitay hain, to kehte hain ke hum imaan laaye hain aur jab alehadgi mein apne shaitano se mlitay hain, to kehte hain ke asal mein to hum tumahray sath hain aur un logon se mehez mazaq kar rahay hain"
2,15,"Allah un se mazaq kar raha hai, woh un ki rassi daraaz kiye jata hai, aur yeh apni sar kashi mein andhon ki terhan bhataktay chalay jatay hain"
2,16,"yeh woh log hain jinhon ne hadaayat ke badlay gumraahi khareed li hai, magar yeh soda un ke liye naffa bakhash nahi hai aur yeh hargiz sahih rastay par nahi hain"
